We enjoy teaching our sweet two year-old how to gently and respectfully treat dogs, especially little guys like me. It’s a lot for an exuberant toddler to learn, so we practice each day. She’s doing great! My favorite part is teaching her how to give me snacks. ⠀
⠀
Then again, I like going for fun walks and just hanging out, too.
